text:
Yeah - this is the cleanest way.
something I'd recommend is to do it like this:
• Use a simple text element(anchor)
• and write your module code like this:
```{% set anchor = module.anchor|lower|replace(' ', '-') %}

&lt;div class="anchor" id="{{ anchor }}"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
{% if is_in_page_editor %}
    &lt;div style="background-color:#eaeaea; padding:.5rem; text-align:center; font-weight:bold;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Anchor: {{ anchor }}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
{% endif %}```
